entries.journal_entry_description: Gendra has asked you to come visit when you have a chance. He has much to teach you about crafting and entertainment professions.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: Hey kid! I see that you made it safely to Tatooine from Tansarii Point Station.  I've got a friend you might be interested in talking to, name's Gendra. Go by and say hi to him. Good luck, kid, and I hope to see ya around!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You should go see Gendra to speak about crafting or entertainer professions.
